3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication channels and interference, which are relevant to the field of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the control of communication channels in the presence of jammers, which is relevant to the field of systems and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - While less likely, the paper deals with the transmission of signals and noise, which could be relevant to the field of multimedia.
